{"article_id":"blqfeP2s6rEAQuyE","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Stung by domestic defeat","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"after a losing battle with Democrats in Washington , D.C. , this winter ,","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"President Donald Trump hopes","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"his negotiating skills can achieve better results some 8,000 miles away","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"when he meets with North Korea ' s leader in Vietnam later this month .","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"Trump will travel for his second session with the North Korean dictator Kim Jong Un","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"to discuss","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"whether the strongman might relinquish his nuclear weapons in return for an end to economic isolation .","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"Skeptics call it a fool ' s errand .","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"But even some harsh critics of Trump ' s foreign policy hold open the possibility","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"that the president might find it easier to deal with the diminutive Asian tyrant than with House Speaker Nancy Pelosi .","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"At a minimum , the Hanoi summit offers Trump a chance","depth":4},{"id":12,"text":"to shift a losing political narrative","depth":5},{"id":13,"text":"which dates back to the drubbing","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"his party took in November ' s midterm elections .","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"\" A lot of positive things are going on , \"","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"Trump insisted in a Friday White House news conference","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"mostly devoted to his frustration","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"that Congress had denied him on the border wall funding","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"he ' d long demanded .","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"\" We ' re working on a summit , \"","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"he added ,","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"predicting","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"that it \" will be a very successful one . \"","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"If so ,","depth":5},{"id":25,"text":"the summit could be a step towards a historic diplomatic achievement","depth":6},{"id":26,"text":"that becomes central to his 2020 reelection pitch .","depth":6},{"id":27,"text":"But another high-profile failure could leave Trump looking dangerously ineffectual .","depth":3},{"id":28,"text":"Playbook newsletter","depth":3},{"id":29,"text":"Sign up today","depth":5},{"id":30,"text":"to receive the # 1-rated newsletter in politics","depth":5},{"id":31,"text":"Email Sign Up","depth":5},{"id":32,"text":"By signing up","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"you agree to receive email newsletters or alerts from .","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"You can unsubscribe at any time .","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"This site is protected by reCAPTCHA","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"and the Google Privacy Policy and Terms of Service apply .","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"\" If he has another summit with Kim Jong Un","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"that doesn ' t really lead to something more serious","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"than what we ' ve seen so far ,","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"having had the debacle of the negotiation with the Congress ,","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"it starts to chip away at his mantra","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"that ' I alone can fix it '","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"and ' I ' m the greatest deal-maker of all time , ' \"","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"said Eric Edelman , a former top Pentagon official under President George W. Bush .","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"\" Democrats are likely to say","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"he pisses off our friends ,","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"cozies up to our enemies","depth":12},{"id":48,"text":"and can ' t negotiate out of a paper bag , much less ' The Art of the Deal , ' \"","depth":12},{"id":49,"text":"Edelman said .","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"If Trump secures real concessions from Kim ,","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"he added ,","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"the president \" can make a plausible case","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"that his methods are unorthodox","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"- but he ' s gotten results . \"","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"While Trump allies concede","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"the partial government shutdown was a setback for the president ,","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"they dismiss talk of a winter of discontent ,","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"noting","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"that Trump ' s Gallup approval rating has bounced from 37 percent during the shutdown to 44 percent this week","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"- just 2 points below his winning 2016 election total .","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"Insisting","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"there is no serious damage","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"to repair ,","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"they say","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"they are measuring the Hanoi summit on its national security merits","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"- as a test","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"of whether North Korea , one of the world ' s most dangerous regimes , can be persuaded to give up a nuclear program","depth":13},{"id":68,"text":"it developed at the cost of decades of deprivation and isolation .","depth":13},{"id":69,"text":"One Republican close to the White House argued","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"that any implications for the president ' s standing are mainly on the upside .","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"Most Americans don ' t pay attention to the details of nuclear diplomacy","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"and are more likely to focus on a stunning success than a continued stalemate .","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"\" I think","depth":13},{"id":74,"text":"it ' s simple :","depth":13},{"id":75,"text":"If it ' s a success ,","depth":14},{"id":76,"text":"they ' ll tout it .","depth":14},{"id":77,"text":"If it ' s not ,","depth":14},{"id":78,"text":"they won ' t , \"","depth":14},{"id":79,"text":"said a Republican close to the White House .","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"\" It ' s historic and incredible","depth":12},{"id":81,"text":"if it works .","depth":12},{"id":82,"text":"It ' s a setback","depth":12},{"id":83,"text":"if it doesn ' t . \"","depth":12},{"id":84,"text":"Skeptics have long scoffed at the possibility","depth":8},{"id":85,"text":"that Trump can persuade Kim to give up his nuclear arsenal ,","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"arguing","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"that the North Korean leader is playing to Trump ' s vanity","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"- including by sending him fawning letters","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"that Trump proudly shows off to Oval Office visitors -","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"while slowly chipping away at his international pariah status .","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"Those critics note","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"that Trump ' s previous summit with Kim , in Singapore last June , was more a media spectacle than a sober diplomatic exchange","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"and produced only a vague statement of shared goals .","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"While Trump declared it an unqualified success ,","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"his administration scaled back expectations weeks before the meeting","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"after the North Koreans rejected a written U.S. proposal","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"laying out a road map for the \" complete , verifiable , and irreversible \" denuclearization","depth":13},{"id":98,"text":"that Trump officials have demanded .","depth":13},{"id":99,"text":"But at least one leading authority on nuclear strategy concedes","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"that Trump might , almost by accident , crack one of the hardest and most dangerous international problems in generations .","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"\" This is not normal diplomacy .","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"But this is not a normal president .","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"Maybe in spite of himself , he has some pretty brilliant ideas , \"","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"said Graham Allison , a longtime nuclear strategist at Harvard University .","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"Trump \" is more like what Kim is .","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"Kim looks at social media ,","depth":12},{"id":107,"text":"watches a basketball game ,","depth":13},{"id":108,"text":"watches some stupid movie .","depth":13},{"id":109,"text":"He is communicating to this young man in ways","depth":12},{"id":110,"text":"he may understand better than a lecture from me , \"","depth":12},{"id":111,"text":"Allison added .","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"Optimists point to recent evidence","depth":8},{"id":113,"text":"that Trump ' s special representative to North Korea , Stephen Biegun has been gaining traction .","depth":8},{"id":114,"text":"After initially struggling to secure meetings with his North Korean counterparts","depth":9},{"id":115,"text":"following his August appointment ,","depth":9},{"id":116,"text":"Beigun has had more success","depth":9},{"id":117,"text":"and has raised his profile in an empowering way .","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"Diplomats and experts took note of a photo","depth":8},{"id":119,"text":"Trump tweeted from the Oval Office on Christmas Eve","depth":9},{"id":120,"text":"showing Biegun , along with National Security Council official Allison Hooker ,","depth":10},{"id":121,"text":"standing beside the Resolute desk","depth":11},{"id":122,"text":"discussing North Korea .","depth":11},{"id":123,"text":"\" Christmas Eve briefing with my team","depth":10},{"id":124,"text":"working on North Korea -","depth":10},{"id":125,"text":"Progress being made , \"","depth":10},{"id":126,"text":"Trump wrote .","depth":10},{"id":127,"text":"\" Looking forward to my next summit with Chairman Kim ! \"","depth":8},{"id":128,"text":"Joel Wit , a senior fellow at the Stimson Center","depth":8},{"id":129,"text":"who helped negotiate a 1994 U.S. nuclear agreement with North Korea ,","depth":8},{"id":130,"text":"called the picture an \" important signal \" to the North Koreans","depth":8},{"id":131,"text":"\" that Biegun can actually see the president of the United States","depth":9},{"id":132,"text":"- and that ' s not a given . \"","depth":9},{"id":133,"text":"In an address at Stanford University last month , Biegun announced","depth":9},{"id":134,"text":"that the North Koreans have taken preliminary steps","depth":10},{"id":135,"text":"to dismantle two sites","depth":12},{"id":136,"text":"used for missile and nuclear testing","depth":12},{"id":137,"text":"and have committed to destroying their plutonium and uranium enrichment facilities .","depth":11},{"id":138,"text":"\" We ' re seeing a gradual evolution of the positions on both sides ,","depth":11},{"id":139,"text":"which is an encouraging sign , \"","depth":11},{"id":140,"text":"Wit said .","depth":10},{"id":141,"text":"\" Certainly there ' s a recognition","depth":11},{"id":142,"text":"that the substantive outcomes have to be more","depth":12},{"id":143,"text":"than they were at the first summit .","depth":12},{"id":144,"text":"I feel like","depth":11},{"id":145,"text":"this is going to be better . \"","depth":11},{"id":146,"text":"Administration officials said","depth":9},{"id":147,"text":"they expect to leave Hanoi with a road map for North Korea ' s denuclearization","depth":10},{"id":148,"text":"that outlines a series of steps","depth":12},{"id":149,"text":"each side can commit to undertaking","depth":12},{"id":150,"text":"in order to achieve that goal .","depth":11},{"id":151,"text":"Biegun hinted at this approach in his remarks ,","depth":9},{"id":152,"text":"telling the audience at Stanford","depth":10},{"id":153,"text":"that the North Koreans were prepared to take action","depth":11},{"id":154,"text":"contingent upon \" the United States taking corresponding measures . \"","depth":11},{"id":155,"text":"Some experts hope","depth":7},{"id":156,"text":"that Trump will walk away","depth":8},{"id":157,"text":"if this summit fails .","depth":8},{"id":158,"text":"\" At least from what I understand","depth":9},{"id":159,"text":"from dealing with this administration ,","depth":9},{"id":160,"text":"they will walk away ,","depth":9},{"id":161,"text":"and I hope","depth":11},{"id":162,"text":"that they will walk away","depth":11},{"id":163,"text":"if they don ' t get something this time , \"","depth":10},{"id":164,"text":"said David Albright , president of the Institute for Science and International Security .","depth":7},{"id":165,"text":"But in his news conference Friday , Trump seemed to have the highest hopes for his meeting with Kim .","depth":6},{"id":166,"text":"Trump even declared","depth":9},{"id":167,"text":"that Japan ' s prime minister , Shinzo Abe , had nominated him for the Nobel Prize in appreciation of his nuclear diplomacy .","depth":9},{"id":168,"text":"Abe \" gave me the most beautiful copy of a letter","depth":10},{"id":169,"text":"that he sent to the people","depth":11},{"id":170,"text":"who give out a thing","depth":12},{"id":171,"text":"called the Nobel Prize .","depth":12},{"id":172,"text":"He said ,","depth":12},{"id":173,"text":"' I have nominated you respectfully on behalf of Japan. '","depth":12},{"id":174,"text":"I said ,","depth":12},{"id":175,"text":"' Thank you ,","depth":13},{"id":176,"text":"many other people feel that way too , ' \"","depth":13},{"id":177,"text":"Trump said .","depth":10},{"id":178,"text":"That claim puzzled analysts","depth":8},{"id":179,"text":"who note","depth":9},{"id":180,"text":"that Tokyo has concerns","depth":10},{"id":181,"text":"that the president ' s apparent eagerness","depth":12},{"id":182,"text":"to cut a deal with Kim","depth":12},{"id":183,"text":"could leave unaddressed Japanese concerns about North Korea ' s short-range missile program .","depth":11},{"id":184,"text":"Even if Trump isn ' t awarded","depth":8},{"id":185,"text":"- or even actually nominated -","depth":8},{"id":186,"text":"for a Nobel Prize ,","depth":7},{"id":187,"text":"he is likely to cast himself as a peacemaker .","depth":6},{"id":188,"text":"\" I believe","depth":8},{"id":189,"text":"he would ' ve gone to war with North Korea , \"","depth":8},{"id":190,"text":"Trump said of President Barack Obama ,","depth":8},{"id":191,"text":"with whom he discussed the North Korean threat","depth":9},{"id":192,"text":"before he took office .","depth":9},{"id":193,"text":"\" I think","depth":9},{"id":194,"text":"he was ready to go to war ,","depth":9},{"id":195,"text":"in fact he told me","depth":10},{"id":196,"text":"he was so close to starting a big war with North Korea , \"","depth":10},{"id":197,"text":"Trump said .","depth":9},{"id":198,"text":"\" Now where are we now ?","depth":8},{"id":199,"text":"No missiles , no rocks , no nuclear testing .","depth":9},{"id":200,"text":"We ' ve learned a lot . \"","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":401,"left":228,"right":400,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":228,"left":215,"right":227,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":215,"left":211,"right":214,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":211,"left":205,"right":210,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":205,"left":202,"right":204,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":202,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":204,"left":203,"right":4,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":203,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":210,"left":207,"right":209,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":207,"left":5,"right":206,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":206,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":209,"left":8,"right":208,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":208,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":214,"left":11,"right":213,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":213,"left":12,"right":212,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":212,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":